room_title: Escape room "Miner Problems" by GTFO Escape Room in South Portland
room_description: You and your group were exploring a cave when all of a sudden there was a MINER PROBLEM! The cave has fallen in and you have been divided from your group. Lucky for you, you and your group have falling into an old mining workshop that has been locked up for safety. Though it looks like the miners might have started playing tricks on each other down in these depths...
